page.title: 18COMMERCIAL DEVELOPMENT,F'bro
page.content: The eastern edge of the block includes an interesting variety of{commercial {development.}To the east of Frimley exists a new{Industrial Estate.}Most of the development is given over to companies which specialise in {technological development}for both {consumer and industrial} defence worlds. This is balanced at the southern part of the block by the {older Farnborough Street area}which includes a variety of{small businesses which have been established for up to {150 yrs}and includes a {baker,building {materials co.,}and a{small sheet metal {works.}The British Car Auctions which started on their present site in {1954 is the most interesting in that it was the first of its kind in the U.K. They currently sell {60000}cars p.a.but are about to move to a new site which will be the biggest in {Europe.}
